title: Update Imagine.R
body:
This is my first contribution, 

so I hope not to break anything!

My suggestion is: in line 77, when plotting species names, adding " las=2 " plots the labels vertically, it helped me to explore species/sites relationships in an easier way. See the attached pdf.

Best,
Pierluigi

[metacom 45678lab.pdf](https://github.com/taddallas/metacom/files/1090724/metacom.45678lab.pdf)

title: Implemented vegan updates & progress bar
body: NullMaker now uses nullmodel() from vegandev 2.1-43 to construct null matrices (much faster). Added progress bar (helps when allow.empty=FALSE). Added new function to identify metacommunity structure based on tests in Metacommunity()

title: Replace while loop & add progress bar
body: Improved efficiency using for loop instead of while loop for NullMaker (can check with system.time, really helps for large matrices) and added a progress bar (default = FALSE) to alert user of progress. Added new function to identify metacommunity structure.
